	* commands/cat.c (grub_cmd_cat): Remove non-ESC keys from keyboard queue
	to ensure that break with ESC will always work.
	* commands/sleep.c (grub_interruptible_millisleep): Likewise.
	Remove ESC from keyboard queue.

