	returning `grub_errno'.

2007-11-03  Marco Gerards  <marco@gnu.org>

	* disk/ata.c (grub_ata_readwrite): Call grub_ata_pio_read and
	grub_ata_pio_write once for every single sector, instead of for
	multiple sectors.

