2006-12-13  Thomas Schwinge  <tschwinge@gnu.org>

	* Makefile.in (enable_grub_emu): New variable.
	* configure.ac (--enable-grub-emu): New option.
	Do the checks for (n)curses only if `--enable-grub-emu' is requested.
